thout even mentioning how much I am obliged to Dr. Kogan-Bernstein,8 whom I would owe over 5000 francs(!) if she were charging me anything (the usual charge for one treatment is 100 frs.!) Try not to worry too much, my love. We shall soon be together anyway.9 Tell Mother I embrace her and am not writing her only because I am spending all my epistolary energy on you.

